Parts are abandon-ware C which have been converted.
Parts are Public Domain which have been ported or converted from C.
Parts are a Library.
Parts allow you to build programs.

So the Licensing is complex.
You can loosen, but you cant tighten.

Overall MIT is the best -and most compatible- License.
FPC Dev team needs to GIT with the program. 
